name: CyberRun (EndLabDominikNa)
description:
This game is a small parkour game where you have to solve small puzzles in a cinematic world.

This game was created for the Brackey's Game Jam 2023.1

Controls:

  • WASD - Movement
  • Space - Jump
  • Left Shift - Sprinting
  • Mouse - Looking
  • Mouse Left Click - open/close pipe
